ldclass in 2024; it\u0026#39;s a nonprofit fashion brand where 100% of profits go toward increasing access to colonoscopies in underserved communities. The brand features a minimalist aesthetic and styles that are as versatile as they are cool, cozy, and comfortable, while also informing shoppers of the importance of early detection.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHero Products: \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=133023X1595699\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldclassclothing.com%2Fproducts%2Fsignature-worldclass-sweatshirt-oyster-fw24%3Fvariant%3D49177282445608\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSignature Women\u0026#39;s Sweatshirt in Oyster\u003c/a\u003e ($119), \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=133023X1595699\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldclassclothing.com%2Fproducts%2Fsignature-sweatpants-in-oyster%3Fvariant%3D49480690401576\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSignature Sweatpants in Oyster\u003c/a\u003e ($95), \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=133023X1595699\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldclassclothing.com%2Fproducts%2Funisex-short-sleeve-ass-t-shirt-copy%3Fvariant%3D49340448702760\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eWomen\u0026#39;s Ringer Tee\u003c/a\u003e ($39)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePR Representation:\u003c/strong\u003e Elle Communications\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to get in touch: \u003c/strong\u003ehello@worldclassclothing.com, press@worldclassclothing.com\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWant your brand featured? Hit the link below.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/page/brand-fo